body_html: This question is better addressed on StackOverflow. Also, your question is ill-posed. Thread safety is not a simple concept. It is more a question of is it thread-safe to use something in a particular way. For someone to answer this question, you need to describe the context in which you are going to be setting up your feedforward prediction infrastructure.
